=3D"https://quillette.com/2019/11/16/thorstein-veblens-theory-of-the-leisur=
e-class-a-status-update/" rel=3D"">article</a><span> in Quillette.&nbsp;</s=
pan></p><p>You won=E2=80=99t find the term anywhere on this Substack.&nbsp;=
</p><p>I don=E2=80=99t use the term. But I always find it interesting that,=
 so incredibly often, it=E2=80=99s what people (particularly cultural elite=
